<script type="text/javascript">
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $('.close-popap').bind('click', function () {
            $('.city-overlay').removeClass('active');
            $('.city-popap').removeClass('active');
        });

        $('.js__open-select-city').click(function () {
            $('#aspnetForm .rcbSlide').hide();
            var winSelected = $('<div class="win-select-city"></div>');
            var selectCityContent = $('.content-win-select-city').html();
            $(winSelected).append(selectCityContent);
            $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list__item[data-city-id=' + $('#sysSelectedBlock input[type=text]').val() + ']').addClass('active');
            $('body').append(winSelected);
            $('.js__close-win-select-city').click(function () {
                $(this).parents('.win-select-city').remove();
                $('#aspnetForm .rcbSlide').hide();
            })

            $(winSelected).find('.input-search-city').bind('input propertychange', function(e)
            {
                var inputSearch = $(this).val();
                $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list__item').css('display', 'block');
                $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list__item-title').css('display', 'block');
                $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list').css('-webkit-column-count', 5);
                $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list').css('-moz-column-count', 5);
                $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list').css('column-count', 5);
                if (inputSearch != '') {
                    $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list__item-title').css('display', 'none');
                    $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list').css('-webkit-column-count', 1);
                    $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list').css('-moz-column-count', 1);
                    $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list').css('column-count', 1);
                    $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list__item').each(function (i, elem) {
                        var text = $(elem).html().toLowerCase();
                        inputSearch = inputSearch.toLowerCase();
                        if (text.indexOf(inputSearch) < 0) {
                            $(elem).css('display', 'none');
                        }
                    });
                }
                return false;
            });

            /* Добавление вначале списка букв */
            var it = '#';
            $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list__item').each(function (i, elem) {
                var contianer = $(elem).find('label').length > 0 ? $(elem).find('label') : $(elem);
                var name = $.trim($(contianer).html()).toLowerCase();
                if (name.charAt(0) != it) {
                    var container = $('<div class="win-select-city__list__container-item-title"></div>');
                    var style = it == '#' ? 'style="margin-top:0;"' : '';
                    it = name.charAt(0);
                    $(container).append('<div class="win-select-city__list__item-title" ' + style + '>' + it.toUpperCase() + '</div>');
                    $(elem).before($(container));
                    $(container).append($(elem));
                }
            });

            /* Выбор нужного города */
            $(winSelected).find('.win-select-city__list__item').click(function (e) {
                var idCity = $(this).attr('data-city-id');
                $('#sysSelectedBlock input[type=text]').val(idCity);
                $('#sysSelectedBlock input[type=submit]').trigger('click');
            })

            return false;
        });
    })
</script>

        $("[data-menu=main-menu-item]").on("mouseenter", function () {
            var $submenu = $(this).find("[data-menu=sub-menu]");

            if ($submenu.hasClass("hide"))
                $submenu.removeClass("hide");
        });

        // убираем подменю если вышли из зоны указателя не на подменю
        $("[data-menu=main-menu-item]").on("mouseleave", function (e) {
            var $submenu = $(this).find("[data-menu=sub-menu]");

            if ($(e.relatedTarget) !== ($submenu)) {
                if (!$submenu.hasClass("hide"))
                    $submenu.addClass("hide");
            }
        });

        // убираем подменю когда его покидают
        $("[data-menu=sub-menu]").on("mouseleave", function (e) {
            var $subMenu = $(this);
            var $parent = $subMenu.parent("[data-menu=main-menu-item]");
            var $target = $(e.relatedTarget);
            if (!$target.is($parent) && !$target.parent().is($parent))
                if (!$subMenu.hasClass("hide"))
                    $(this).addClass("hide");
        });
    });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
    function ChangeCatalogVid(vid) {
        var vidTableSpan = $('#lev2-catalog-vid-table');
        var vidListSpan = $('#lev2-catalog-vid-list');
        if (vid == 'table') {
            $('#lev2-cont').removeClass('lev2-list').addClass('lev2-table');
            vidTableSpan.addClass('selected');
            vidListSpan.removeClass('selected');
        }
        if (vid == 'list') {
            $('#lev2-cont').removeClass('lev2-table').addClass('lev2-list');
            vidListSpan.addClass('selected');
            vidTableSpan.removeClass('selected');
        }
        $.cookie("catalog_view", vid, { expires: 7 });
    }
    var ecommerceImpressions = [];
    var addedProducts = [];
    var listGAProduct = {};
    // Переход на просмотр товара
    var onInfoProduct = function (dataClick) {
        window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
        dataLayer.push({
            'ecommerce': {
                'currencyCode': 'RUB',
                'click': {
                    'actionField': { 'list': 'Просмотр из каталога' },
                    'products': [dataClick]
                }
            },
            'event': 'gtm-ee-event',
            'event-category': 'EEcommerce',
            'event-action': 'Product Clicks',
            'event-non-interaction': 'False',
        });
    }

    // Добавление в корзину SV
    var onAddProduct = function (dataClick) {
        var addedProductstr = $(dataClick).parents('.img-btn-cont').attr('data-json');
        addedProduct = JSON.parse(addedProductstr);
        addedProducts.push(addedProduct);
        window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
        dataLayer.push({
            'ecommerce': {
                'currencyCode': 'RUB',
                'add': {

                    'actionField': { 'list': 'Просмотр из каталога' },
                    'products': addedProducts
                }
            },
            'event': 'gtm-ee-event',
            'event-category': 'EEcommerce',
            'event-action': 'Adding a Product to a Shopping Cart',
            'event-non-interaction': 'False',

        });
    }

    // функция проверки полной видимости элемента
    var checkPosition = function (item) {
        var data = $(item).data('item');

        if (ecommerceImpressions.indexOf(data, 0) != -1)
        { return; } else {
            var div_position = $(item).offset();
            var div_top = div_position.top;
            var div_left = div_position.left;
            var div_width = $(item).width();
            var div_height = $(item).height();

            var top_scroll = $(document).scrollTop();
            var left_scroll = $(document).scrollLeft();

            var screen_width = $(window).width();
            var screen_height = $(window).height();

            var see_x1 = left_scroll;
            var see_x2 = screen_width + left_scroll;
            var see_y1 = top_scroll;
            var see_y2 = screen_height + top_scroll;

            var div_x1 = div_left;
            var div_x2 = div_left + div_width;
            var div_y1 = div_top;
            var div_y2 = div_top + div_height;

            // проверка - виден полностью или нет
            if (div_x1 >= see_x1 && div_x2 <= see_x2 && div_y1 >= see_y1 && div_y2 <= see_y2) {
                // если виден
                ecommerceImpressions.push(data);
                window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
                dataLayer.push({
                    'ecommerce': {
                        'currencyCode': 'RUB',
                        'impressions': ecommerceImpressions,
                    },
                    'event': 'gtm-ee-event',
                    'event-category': 'EEcommerce',
                    'event-action': ' Product Impressions',
                    'event-non-interaction': 'True',
                })
            }
        }
    }

    // функция прогона элементов по проверке
    // при скролинге и изменении размера экрана
    var bindCheckPosition = function () {
        // var arrItems = $('[data-item]');
        window.listCheckPositionAtGAProduct = $('[data-item]');
        for (var i = 0; i < listCheckPositionAtGAProduct.length; i++) {
            checkPosition(listCheckPositionAtGAProduct[i]);
        }
        $(document).scroll(function () {
            listCheckPositionAtGAProduct.each(function () {
                checkPosition(this);
            })
        });
        $(window).resize(function () {
            listCheckPositionAtGAProduct.each(function () {
                checkPosition(this);
            })
        });
    }
    // наблюдение за имзенением элеменетов в блоке
    var MutationObserver = window.MutationObserver || window.WebKitMutationObserver || window.MozMutationObserver;
    var observer = new MutationObserver(function (mutations) {
        mutations.forEach(function (mutation) {
            window.listCheckPositionAtGAProduct = $('[data-item]');
        });
    });
    $(document).ready(function () {
        bindCheckPosition();
        // привязываем налюдение на блок
        var list = document.querySelector('.cat-lev2 > div');
        if (list != null) {
            observer.observe(list, {
                attributes: false,
                childList: true,
                characterData: true
            });
        }
    });

</script>

            var header = $(this).parents('.category-condition').find('.condition-head');

            if (!(header.hasClass('some-class-active')))
                header.addClass('some-class-active');
        });
    }
    var toggleActiveBlock = function () {
        $('.category-condition__body').each(function () {
            if ($(this).find('[type="checkbox"]:checked').length > 0) {
                $(this).prevAll('.condition-head').addClass('condition-head-up');
                $(this).show();
            }
        });
    }

    Sys.Application.add_load(ApplicationLoadHandler)
    function ApplicationLoadHandler(sender, args) {
        Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_initializeRequest(CheckStatus);
        Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(EndRequest);
    }
    function CheckStatus(sender, args) {
        var prm = Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance();
        if (prm.get_isInAsyncPostBack()) {
            prm.abortPostBack();
        }
    }
    function SetOverlay() {
        $('.cat-lev2').fadeOut('slow');
        $('.cat-lev2-overlay').fadeIn('slow');
    }
    function EndRequest(sender, args) {
        LoadSlider();
        $('.cat-lev2').fadeIn('slow');
        $('.cat-lev2-overlay').fadeOut('fast');
        checkSelectionBlock();
        toggleActiveBlock();
    }
    function stopAndStartTimer(timeout) {
        window.clearTimeout(timer);
        timer = window.setTimeout(function () { $('.go-search').click(); }, timeout);
    }
    $(function () {
        var isFullSearch = 'False' == 'False' ? false : true;
        LoadSlider();
        toggleActiveBlock();
        $(".filter-content").slideDown(300);

        $('.filter-zone').on('click', '[data-btn="ibSearch"]', function () {
            stopAndStartTimer(500);
        });
        $('.filter-zone').on('click', '[data-category="heder"] .condition-head', function () {
            var _this = this;
            var codition = $(_this).next('[data-category="codition"]');
            up_Down();
            function up_Down() {
                var head = $(_this);

                if (head.hasClass('condition-head-up'))
                    head.removeClass('condition-head-up');
                else
                    head.addClass('condition-head-up');
            }
            
            if ($(codition).find('input[checked=checked]').length > 0) {
                $(codition).find('td').each(function()
                {
                    if ($(this).find('input[checked=checked]').length < 1) {
                        $(this).fadeToggle('fast');
                    }
                })
            } else {
                $(_this).next('[data-category="codition"]')
                    .fadeToggle('fast');
            }
        });
        $('.filter-zone').on('click', 'input[type=checkbox]', function () {
            if (!isFullSearch) {
                stopAndStartTimer(1400);
                checkSelectionBlock();
            }
        });
    });
</script>
